1
00:01:30,830 --> 00:01:34,979
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:39,520
[2010]

3
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,039
Feel free to look around here.

4
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:39,840
Let me know if you need anything.

5
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:43,280
Hello.

6
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:44,310
Is there any layout

7
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:45,570
you are interested in?

8
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,229
Hello.

9
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,509
I'd like to ask,

10
00:01:47,590 --> 00:01:49,229
how much is the smallest unit here?

11
00:01:49,229 --> 00:01:50,120
Here's our floor plan.

12
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,150
Please take a look.

13
00:01:51,150 --> 00:01:54,210
The down payment for the smallest unit
is 800,000 yuan.

14
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:55,950
Okay.

15
00:01:55,970 --> 00:01:57,070
Take a look first.

16
00:01:57,070 --> 00:01:58,870
Let me know if you need anything.

17
00:01:59,310 --> 00:01:59,920
Hello.

18
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:01,090
Any layout you're interested in?

19
00:02:01,090 --> 00:02:02,150
You can take a look.

20
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,690
Come on, take a look.

21
00:02:04,010 --> 00:02:05,680
These are three-bedroom,
two-living-room units.

22
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,790
The layouts are excellent,

23
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:08,150
with great north-south ventilation.

24
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,590
We've got very well-developed

25
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:11,790
surrounding facilities and greenery.

26
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:13,190
The units on that side
have already sold out.

27
00:02:13,190 --> 00:02:14,590
Only this section is still available now.

28
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:15,000
Yes.

29
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,680
It's a very popular layout.

30
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:18,360
[Episode 12]
[Don't Look Down on the Poor Youth]

31
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,530
Here you are.

32
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,360
Okay, thanks.

33
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:27,560
Did the call get through?

34
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,420
It got through,

35
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,840
but the subdistrict office said

36
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,840
they can't reach her family either.

37
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:32,910
I figured.

38
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:36,079
The rental agent mentioned before

39
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:38,160
that Granny Yu only has one son,

40
00:02:38,290 --> 00:02:39,400
who took his wife and child

41
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,560
abroad

42
00:02:40,590 --> 00:02:41,590
over 20 years ago.

43
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,600
There hasn't been any news of them since.

44
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,000
Granny Yu just stayed in the house,

45
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,560
waiting for him to come back.

46
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,590
Granny Yu used to be

47
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:49,470
a young lady from a prominent family.

48
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:50,870
She's quite stubborn.

49
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,400
I guess she took her medicine

50
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,960
and got injections in secret,

51
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,710
not wanting us to see

52
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,910
her vulnerable side.

53
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:01,960
Let's go.

54
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:22,880
You're awake.

55
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:23,940
How do you feel?

56
00:03:24,050 --> 00:03:24,750
I'll call the doctor.

57
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:25,840
I want dim sum.

58
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:27,800
Okay.

59
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,360
I'll go buy some.

60
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:36,910
Granny.

61
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,310
That's your granddaughter, right?

62
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:40,650
She sent her mom home to sleep last night

63
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,660
and stayed by your side all night herself.

64
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:43,660
That young lady

65
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,240
is both pretty and filial.

66
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,300
You're so blessed.

67
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,680
She's not my granddaughter.

68
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,370
Can Granny Yu really eat

69
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:53,000
these pastries you bought?

70
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,590
Since Granny Yu specifically
asked for them,

71
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:55,990
I have to buy them anyway.

72
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,530
Don't worry. I've got a way.

73
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:00,240
Comrade Liu Fen.

74
00:04:00,530 --> 00:04:01,260
Xia Xiaolan.

75
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,910
Mr. Tang.

76
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,840
What a coincidence—

77
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,150
to run into each other

78
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:07,610
in a place like a hospital.

79
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,740
Mayor Tang,

80
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,150
I'll go get the car.

81
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:10,840
Please wait a moment.

82
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,170
Okay.

83
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,900
Mr. Tang, are you here for a check-up?

84
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,390
It's nothing serious.

85
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,790
Thanks for your concern.

86
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,630
What's going on with you two?

87
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:21,959
Who's not feeling well?

88
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:22,870
It's not us.

89
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,690
Our landlord is in the hospital,

90
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,950
so we went to buy her some breakfast.

91
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,390
You guys are truly kind-hearted.

92
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,430
You always lend a hand to

93
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,630
anyone who's in trouble.

94
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:32,360
I really should learn from you.

95
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:34,560
Mr. Tang,

96
00:04:34,810 --> 00:04:35,950
since there's nothing else,

97
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,070
we'll head up now.

98
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,680
We still need to deliver breakfast
to Granny Yu.

99
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,270
Alright.

100
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,980
Oh right, Xia Xiaolan.

101
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,170
I remember

102
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,000
you were planning to open

103
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,070
a clothing store, right?

104
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:44,510
Yes.

105
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,000
Has it opened yet?

106
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:47,430
We're still preparing.

107
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:48,830
We don't want to just open

108
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:49,870
a run-of-the-mill little shop.

109
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,670
We're aiming to open a boutique.

110
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:53,750
Well, you really are
quite forward-thinking.

111
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:54,870
Shengcheng

112
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,070
is developing

113
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,070
very rapidly right now.

114
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:58,070
It definitely needs

115
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,750
some high-quality boutiques.

116
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:00,950
If you encounter any difficulties,

117
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,610
have your mother come find me.

118
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,070
Well, we'll head up then.

119
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:06,400
Okay.

120
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:06,890
Okay.

121
00:05:06,890 --> 00:05:07,430
Thank you, Mr. Tang.

122
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:07,960
Goodbye.

123
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:08,600
Goodbye.

124
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:12,650
Goodbye.

125
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:13,360
Goodbye.

126
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:14,600
Mom.

127
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:17,030
Since when did you and Mayor Tang

128
00:05:17,030 --> 00:05:17,960
become so close?

129
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:21,320
He even said things like
"have your mother come find me"?

130
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,680
Well, your auntie

131
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,310
sent us a lot of

132
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,830
specialties from Yunan, right?

133
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:26,560
I knew he used to work in Yunan,

134
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,720
so I gave him some.

135
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:29,400
Xiaolan,

136
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,630
are you able to rent that shop?

137
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,970
I haven't found the owner yet.

138
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,770
I'll figure something out.

139
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,159
Shrimp dumplings,

140
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,920
red bean cake with orange peel,

141
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,630
barbecue pork buns,

142
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,950
and Shumai.

143
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,310
Granny Yu,

144
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:51,480
I bought all this dim sum

145
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,090
from Lan Kwai Restaurant for you.

146
00:05:53,090 --> 00:05:53,840
The doctor says

147
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,630
you need protein right now.

148
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:57,800
As for these high-sugar treats,

149
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,750
you can eat them,

150
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,920
but if you do,

151
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,240
you'll have to stay in the hospital
longer.

152
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,980
The choice is yours.

153
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:05,360
Will you eat these,

154
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:06,720
or these?

155
00:06:07,130 --> 00:06:08,570
These eggs and soy milk

156
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,530
are also from Lan Kwai Restaurant.

157
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,510
L-Let me help you.

158
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:21,760
I'll peel it for you.

159
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,720
Your daughter is really something—

160
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:27,980
so young,

161
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:30,980
yet she has so many thoughtful ways
of taking care of people.

162
00:06:30,980 --> 00:06:33,310
Granny Yu, I'll take that as a compliment.

163
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,310
Don't waste these.

164
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,110
I'll eat them.

165
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,480
I'll finish these.

166
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:41,720
Here.

167
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,050
It's really delicious.

168
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:45,190
Granny Yu.

169
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,270
Lan Kwai Restaurant is really nice.

170
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,480
You really have great taste.

171
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,270
Is it that good?

172
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:49,120
Have a taste. Here.

173
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:49,450
Okay.

174
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,950
It's good, right?

175
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:54,280
It's really delicious.

176
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:58,840
♪ Along the long road ahead,
how much beauty awaits ♪

177
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:02,460
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

178
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:07,220
♪ Why pause and look back? ♪

179
00:07:07,790 --> 00:07:11,060
♪ My heart feels so confused ♪

180
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:09,040
You're here.

181
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:09,600
Let me tell you,

182
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,720
there's so much work to do.

183
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,680
Sis Bai and I have been so busy

184
00:07:11,650 --> 00:07:15,520
♪ Silently, I watch the clouds
drift in the sky ♪

185
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,480
that we haven't even had a bite to eat.

186
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,510
You're certainly enthusiastic.

187
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:14,720
But aren't you supposed to be
taking care of your own shop?

188
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,190
Sis Bai's junior is watching it.

189
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:17,330
[Zhenzhu Building Materials Shop]

190
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:20,640
♪ Just like you and I,
our ambitions reach far and wide ♪

191
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:17,160
Sis Bai.

192
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:18,240
Come on. They're here.

193
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,000
Xiaolan!

194
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,680
Xiaolan!

195
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:24,620
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

196
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,120
I finally opened my own shop!

197
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,430
I'm so happy!

198
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,010
Zhenzhu.

199
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:25,830
Congratulations.

200
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:29,840
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

201
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,800
Thank you.

202
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:29,890
And this.

203
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,800
What's this?

204
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:34,470
♪ The road ahead is full of storms ♪

205
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,510
Xiaolan thought for a long time

206
00:07:32,510 --> 00:07:33,560
about what gift to get you.

207
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,070
She decided to give you a landline.

208
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:38,380
♪ I'll get by them one by one ♪

209
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:37,330
Someone will come to install it soon.

210
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,920
That's a big gift.

211
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:40,630
Oh my god.

212
00:07:39,370 --> 00:07:43,380
♪ We'll guard each other
on the road ahead ♪

213
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:42,480
This is too expensive.

214
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,870
In all of Renmin Bridge,

215
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,159
few people have landlines.

216
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:47,170
♪ Don't be afraid of the long path ♪

217
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,070
I have a pager,

218
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:47,270
which is already very convenient.

219
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:48,159
Isn't that perfect?

220
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:51,510
♪ With you,
there won't be despair on this path ♪

221
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,480
Zhenzhu Building Materials

222
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,310
is leading the way in Renmin Bridge again.

223
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,870
With a landline, it's easier
to stay in touch.

224
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:56,480
♪ With you, my faith grows stronger ♪

225
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,040
And it can even bring in some income.

226
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,700
If anyone wants to make a call,

227
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,850
you can charge them 2 dimes per minute.

228
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,270
Xiaolan.

229
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,630
Why are you so smart?

230
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:01,810
I'll accept it.

231
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:03,750
You've been renting the shop

232
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,600
and stocking up recently.

233
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,240
If there's anything

234
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,060
you need help with,

235
00:08:06,060 --> 00:08:06,990
just let me know.

236
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:07,760
Right.

237
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:08,430
You can tell us too.

238
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,390
We also made some money

239
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,480
from our business before.

240
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,800
Don't hesitate.

241
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:13,920
I won't hesitate.

242
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,160
You can't imagine how happy I am.

243
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,120
Come on. Come on in.

244
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,270
Let me show you around.

245
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:17,870
Over here,

246
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,680
I plan to display lighting fixtures.

247
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,340
Here, here.

248
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,290
Come over here.

249
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,730
I'll put paint here,

250
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,720
tiles there,

251
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,600
and some small furniture in the middle.

252
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,600
What do you think?

253
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,000
Zhenzhu.

254
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,870
Your shop isn't very big.

255
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,070
You'd better focus on one category,

256
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:34,270
something distinctive

257
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,240
that sets your shop apart

258
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,240
from other shops.

259
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,409
One category...

260
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:40,390
How about lighting fixtures?

261
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:41,320
There are so many types

262
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,720
of lighting fixtures nowadays.

263
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,840
Before, to buy a lamp,

264
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,750
you had to go to Longcheng

265
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:45,550
or Jingcheng.

266
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:46,870
Lighting fixtures will be
my shop's specialty,

267
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:48,840
but I want to sell other products too.

268
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,150
After all, when people come all the way
to Renmin Bridge,

269
00:08:50,150 --> 00:08:51,030
they'd want to

270
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:51,600
bring more things home,

271
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,030
right?

272
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:55,680
Xiaolan.

273
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,750
When Zhenzhu asked you just now,

274
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,690
you'd already decided to suggest

275
00:08:58,690 --> 00:09:00,030
she focus on selling lighting fixtures,
right?

276
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:01,630
Why didn't you just tell her?

277
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:03,720
If I told her everything,

278
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:05,270
she would just rely on me.

279
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,930
Sis Bai is actually very smart.

280
00:09:06,930 --> 00:09:08,240
She catches on quickly.

281
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,000
In business,

282
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,750
you have to rely on yourself.

283
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:12,960
Boss,

284
00:09:13,350 --> 00:09:15,530
two orders of barbecue pork rice

285
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:17,120
and one order of pig trotter rice, please.

286
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:17,600
Okay.

287
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,150
Not giving direct advice

288
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:22,030
was both to let Bai Zhenzhu

289
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,230
think independently

290
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:24,960
and because I'm afraid—

291
00:09:25,570 --> 00:09:26,720
afraid that getting too involved in

292
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,850
someone else's life

293
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,460
could lead to unexpected consequences.

294
00:09:31,860 --> 00:09:33,080
There are quite a few dietary restrictions

295
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,960
for diabetics.

296
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,750
So what can and can't she eat?

297
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:36,890
Could you tell me again?

298
00:09:36,890 --> 00:09:37,550
I've already written it down.

299
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:38,480
Just take a look.

300
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,120
Okay, thank you.

301
00:09:40,850 --> 00:09:41,780
Granny Yu.

302
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,090
Don't argue with me.

303
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,720
Just have a good rest for now.

304
00:09:50,170 --> 00:09:50,930
Pay the fees

305
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,120
and she can be discharged.

306
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:52,910
Okay, thanks.

307
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:53,720
Thanks, Doctor.

308
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,440
I'll pay.

309
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:55,880
You...

310
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,240
What a stubborn old lady.

311
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,690
Give it to me.

312
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:16,670
How is it?

313
00:10:16,690 --> 00:10:19,950
We've kept the courtyard
in pretty good shape, haven't we?

314
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,160
Where are you going?

315
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,390
I haven't swept the streets in days.

316
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:28,590
I'll go notify the subdistrict office.

317
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:29,870
Don't worry about it.

318
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:31,160
You just got out of the hospital.

319
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:33,000
I already spoke to the subdistrict office

320
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,960
about your hospitalization

321
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,400
and had them hire a substitute.

322
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,240
But don't worry—

323
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,550
I specifically told them

324
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:39,480
the substitute is temporary.

325
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:42,780
The job is still yours
now that you've been discharged.

326
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:47,640
Five dimes a day...

327
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,600
Two days...

328
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:51,330
What is Granny Yu calculating?

329
00:10:52,030 --> 00:10:53,360
She's calculating how much pay she missed

330
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,160
during her days in the hospital.

331
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:55,960
She just got discharged

332
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,510
and can't start working immediately.

333
00:10:57,510 --> 00:11:00,510
She has to factor in the losses
for the days ahead, too.

334
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,960
Go tell the subdistrict office

335
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,290
to fire the substitute.

336
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,870
I'll sweep the streets myself tomorrow.

337
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:07,440
Okay.

338
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,750
My... My broom...

339
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:24,960
Good morning, Granny Yu.

340
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,770
Did you take your medicine today?

341
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:31,720
That's no way to greet someone.

342
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:33,540
Give me the broom.

343
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,550
I've already finished sweeping for you.

344
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:36,790
I made millet porridge this morning.

345
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:37,850
I'll get you a bowl.

346
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:39,550
Get me a bowl of millet porridge too.

347
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:40,000
Yong.

348
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,000
Hello, Granny Yu.

349
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:42,480
Yong.

350
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:44,840
How's it going with the shop?

351
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,720
Were you able to rent it?

352
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,440
That's what I came to talk to you about.

353
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,130
It can only be rented

354
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:49,480
if the other owner of that shop

355
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:51,150
on 27th Road agrees.

356
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,050
I'm planning to go with Xiaolan

357
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:54,170
and Chen Xiliang

358
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,450
to discuss it again

359
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,200
with Mr. Yuan,

360
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,320
to show our sincerity

361
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,000
and see if he can

362
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,750
give us that person's information.

363
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:00,150
Okay.

364
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:00,720
Alright.

365
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,390
Come have breakfast then.

366
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:01,920
Hurry up.

367
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:02,810
Granny Yu.

368
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,570
I'll bring it in for you in a bit.

369
00:12:11,150 --> 00:12:11,870
Guys.

370
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,960
I can feel

371
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:15,390
your sincerity.

372
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:16,720
But as I said,

373
00:12:17,380 --> 00:12:19,290
since the other owner of this shop

374
00:12:19,310 --> 00:12:20,000
disagrees,

375
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,720
I can't rent it to you.

376
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,000
Mr. Yuan.

377
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:23,630
Please help us

378
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:24,760
contact them again.

379
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:27,270
If it's really too difficult for you,

380
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:28,670
just give their address and phone number

381
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:29,150
to us.

382
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:30,030
We'll contact them ourselves.

383
00:12:30,030 --> 00:12:30,600
Okay?

384
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:31,000
Yeah.

385
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:33,050
We can go find them ourselves.

386
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,720
If they still disagree in person,

387
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,050
then... Then we'll see.

388
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,840
It's not like there's just

389
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,340
this one vacant shop in Shengcheng.

390
00:12:39,340 --> 00:12:40,750
If you had used this time to look around,

391
00:12:40,750 --> 00:12:41,750
you could have probably rented

392
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:43,150
another shop.

393
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:44,840
Mr. Yuan.

394
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,080
What we want to open

395
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,620
is the first branded clothing store
in the country.

396
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:50,170
We have to rent the best

397
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,600
and most prominent shop.

398
00:12:51,870 --> 00:12:53,000
The one on 27th Road

399
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:54,240
is truly the best

400
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,030
we can find.

401
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:55,870
Look.

402
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,910
Isn't this just a dead end?

403
00:12:59,360 --> 00:12:59,910
Come in.

404
00:13:04,270 --> 00:13:04,870
Director,

405
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:07,080
the property owner is here.

406
00:13:07,450 --> 00:13:08,850
Hurry up and bring her in.

407
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:12,670
This is weird.

408
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,190
This other owner

409
00:13:14,310 --> 00:13:15,370
came here herself.

410
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,200
Granny Yu?

411
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,030
Granny Yu,

412
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:52,910
so you are the other owner?

413
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,150
I guess you've

414
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:58,350
had your eye on that shop for a long time.

415
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:58,960
That's why

416
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,620
you rented my house, isn't it?

417
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:01,550
No.

418
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,490
Granny Yu,

419
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,630
I really didn't know

420
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:05,030
the shop belonged to you.

421
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,200
Now that I know,

422
00:14:06,910 --> 00:14:07,550
I still want

423
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:08,750
to ask you—

424
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:10,790
are you willing to rent the shop

425
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:12,450
to us to open a clothing store?

426
00:14:15,930 --> 00:14:17,320
I think you knew all along

427
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,580
that the shop was mine.

428
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:20,550
I swear,

429
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,830
I really didn't know.

430
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:27,670
So you've decided to rent that shop?

431
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:28,720
Yes.

432
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,270
I must rent it.

433
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,200
Sis Bai.

434
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:34,870
I'll put them here for you.

435
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,600
Okay.

436
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:41,150
This calculator is quite expensive.

437
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:42,550
Be gentle, okay?

438
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:44,720
If it breaks, we have to buy a new one.

439
00:14:44,830 --> 00:14:45,480
I thought

440
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,910
it would be easier to do business
with acquaintances.

441
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:48,030
I got ripped off.

442
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:49,120
Who are you talking about?

443
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,550
That lamp seller from Longcheng?

444
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:51,270
Yes, him.

445
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:53,070
I've learned my lesson now.

446
00:14:53,070 --> 00:14:54,390
No matter how close you are,

447
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:56,720
you must think twice
before making a deal.

448
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,720
A fall into a pit, a gain in your wit.

449
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,270
Granny Yu.

450
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:03,550
I agree to your conditions.

451
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:06,150
The rent is 2,000 yuan a year.

452
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,680
Have you thought it through?

453
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:09,480
Xia,

454
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,840
2,000 yuan is a bit expensive.

455
00:15:12,670 --> 00:15:13,930
Not only will I rent it,

456
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:16,070
but I will rent it for 10 years.

457
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:18,510
Ten years?

458
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:21,440
You want the rent to stay the same
for 10 years?

459
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:24,410
The rent will increase by 10% every year.

460
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:26,120
The first year is 2,000 yuan,

461
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,650
the second year 2,200 yuan,

462
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:28,440
the third year

463
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,840
2,420 yuan.

464
00:15:30,190 --> 00:15:31,550
And by the last year of the lease,

465
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,080
I will pay

466
00:15:32,090 --> 00:15:33,840
4,715.9 yuan.

467
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,100
That's it then.

468
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:38,080
Deal.

469
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:41,910
But I have an additional condition.

470
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,150
What condition?

471
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:48,680
I want the right of first refusal
for the shop.

472
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:50,790
Xiaolan.

473
00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:53,010
Granny Yu went out this afternoon

474
00:15:53,010 --> 00:15:54,410
and hasn't come back yet.

475
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,440
Granny Yu, you look so beautiful today.

476
00:15:59,630 --> 00:16:01,830
Did you two run into each other just now?

477
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:04,270
Granny Yu is now our

478
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:05,440
double landlord.

479
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:07,750
Don't tell me that shop

480
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:09,120
belongs to Granny Yu.

481
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:15,200
All 3 parties were there today,

482
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:17,460
so we checked the contract and signed it.

483
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,240
Granny Yu.

484
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:19,270
Thank you.

485
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:21,750
You should know

486
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,270
the 2,000 yuan annual rent

487
00:16:24,270 --> 00:16:25,600
is what I asked from you.

488
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,960
Why are you thanking me?

489
00:16:29,150 --> 00:16:29,840
Girl,

490
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:32,030
don't think you're so lucky.

491
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:33,760
The road ahead of you

492
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:35,440
is still long.

493
00:16:41,190 --> 00:16:42,790
She doesn't seem very happy.

494
00:16:44,270 --> 00:16:45,400
She probably thinks

495
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,850
I found out somewhere

496
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:47,930
about the info

497
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,480
of that shop's owner,

498
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:51,080
and that's why we came

499
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,140
to rent this house—

500
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,370
just to get close to her step by step

501
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,840
in order to get that shop.

502
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:59,270
She feels her feelings were cheated.

503
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:00,320
When she asked for the rent,

504
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,980
she didn't go easy on us at all.

505
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:04,030
We have to explain this clearly to her.

506
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:05,920
When we rented this house back then,

507
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,550
we just wanted to open a small shop.

508
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:09,490
We didn't know about that shop at all.

509
00:17:09,490 --> 00:17:11,210
We think it's a coincidence,

510
00:17:11,430 --> 00:17:12,890
but Granny Yu won't buy it.

511
00:17:13,069 --> 00:17:13,920
There hasn't been news of

512
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,520
her own son for over a decade.

513
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:16,640
How can you expect her to trust

514
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:19,099
the two of us,
whom she just happened to meet?

515
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,200
But it's okay.

516
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:23,000
We're renting the shop for 10 years,

517
00:17:23,119 --> 00:17:25,089
and we'll continue living in this house.

518
00:17:25,089 --> 00:17:26,290
We have plenty of time

519
00:17:26,349 --> 00:17:27,810
to warm Granny Yu's heart.

520
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:32,720
Uncle.

521
00:17:33,040 --> 00:17:33,890
The exterior

522
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:35,380
doesn't need big changes.

523
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:36,480
But these spots

524
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:37,400
must be changed into

525
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,200
this kind of transparent glass
display windows,

526
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,240
so that anyone passing by

527
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,720
can see the new styles inside at a glance.

528
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:42,120
Got it.

529
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:44,030
Besides the interior decoration,

530
00:17:44,030 --> 00:17:45,790
we also need a temperature control system

531
00:17:45,790 --> 00:17:47,110
and a special lighting design.

532
00:17:45,890 --> 00:17:49,670
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

533
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,880
Do you think that will work?

534
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:49,510
Xiaolan,

535
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:50,770
this design of yours

536
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:53,110
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

537
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,350
is even fancier

538
00:17:52,350 --> 00:17:53,170
than Blue Phoenix in Jingcheng.

539
00:17:53,170 --> 00:17:53,830
I have to go back

540
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:54,960
and study this carefully.

541
00:17:53,890 --> 00:17:56,190
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

542
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:57,110
I must ensure we get the effect you want.

543
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:57,480
Okay.

544
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:58,510
Uncle.

545
00:17:58,890 --> 00:18:03,090
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

546
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:00,920
Zhenzhu is selling building materials now.

547
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:02,110
If we need anything,

548
00:18:02,110 --> 00:18:02,970
we can tell her.

549
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,590
She'll definitely give us the best.

550
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:06,500
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

551
00:18:04,930 --> 00:18:06,480
If our renovation turns out well,

552
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,680
it'll be good publicity for her shop too.

553
00:18:06,530 --> 00:18:10,270
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

554
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:08,480
Okay.

555
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,740
I'll go get the measurements now.

556
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:13,240
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

557
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:22,080
Granny Yu, you're back.

558
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,500
Did you take your medicine today?

559
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,400
I did, I did.

560
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:30,670
Who asks others every day

561
00:18:30,700 --> 00:18:32,300
if they took their medicine?

562
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:34,970
Look what a sweet talker your daughter is.

563
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,480
You should learn from her.

564
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,000
Okay,

565
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:38,530
I'll learn from her.

566
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,680
I made noodles today.

567
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,210
Do you want to eat together?

568
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,420
I'll eat in my own room.

569
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:52,440
Mom!

570
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:54,200
Good news.

571
00:18:54,540 --> 00:18:56,070
Our business license has been approved.

572
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:56,660
Really?

573
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:57,440
Look.

574
00:18:58,700 --> 00:18:59,670
This is great.

575
00:18:58,870 --> 00:19:00,810
[Individual Business License]

576
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:02,590
It's just that

577
00:19:03,070 --> 00:19:04,870
I haven't worked for a long time.

578
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:06,650
I'm worried I won't get used to it.

579
00:19:06,650 --> 00:19:07,550
I still need to adapt

580
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:08,240
and learn.

581
00:19:09,380 --> 00:19:10,780
And once I start working,

582
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:11,750
Granny Yu...

583
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:14,670
Don't worry. Just go to work.

584
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:15,990
I'm not so old that

585
00:19:15,990 --> 00:19:18,520
I need someone following me around
every day.

586
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:21,070
Put some vinegar in my noodles.

587
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:22,110
Got it.

588
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,160
Hello, Manager Liu.

589
00:19:28,550 --> 00:19:29,030
Hello.

590
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:30,350
Welcome.

591
00:19:32,530 --> 00:19:33,240
Morning, Boss.

592
00:19:32,930 --> 00:19:36,240
[Zhenzhu Building Materials Shop]

593
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:33,870
Take care.

594
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:34,870
Come by again.

595
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:37,860
Junior.

596
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,680
What was the bottom price

597
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,350
that Mr. Zhou quoted us last time?

598
00:19:41,350 --> 00:19:42,750
If it's higher than our cost,

599
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:43,680
let's go with it.

600
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:46,160
But we'd hardly make any profit like this.

601
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:48,310
We'll just have to learn from this loss.

602
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:50,510
We've got to recover the losses
bit by bit.

603
00:19:50,510 --> 00:19:51,550
Sis Bai.

604
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,240
You're here, Wei.

605
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:55,270
Busy?

606
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:56,960
Yes.

607
00:19:58,350 --> 00:19:59,550
I have some good news.

608
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:00,780
Want to hear it?

609
00:20:01,320 --> 00:20:02,520
What good news?

610
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:03,810
Acting so mysterious.

611
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:05,960
I don't take on anything
that doesn't turn a profit.

612
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:07,640
If I end up losing money,
I'll send you back to Jingcheng.

613
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:09,370
You'll definitely make money.

614
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:12,160
And I'm talking big money.

615
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:13,840
Come here.

616
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:14,640
Let me tell you.

617
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,440
Hurry, hurry.

618
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,400
Come on.

619
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:19,720
Bring it out.

620
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:22,320
Check it out.

621
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:24,510
Good for you!

622
00:20:24,970 --> 00:20:26,000
Transistor radios

623
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,260
are really trendy now.

624
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,400
Where did you get it?

625
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:29,860
Let me tell you.

626
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,320
These all came from the factory's

627
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:32,640
quality control rejects.

628
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,350
But you know what?
After replacing the parts,

629
00:20:34,350 --> 00:20:35,550
they work perfectly.

630
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:37,070
If you're still unsure,

631
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:38,480
we can test a few more.

632
00:20:39,350 --> 00:20:40,350
It's 90 yuan each,

633
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:42,610
and there are 500 pieces in total.

634
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:44,770
I can't handle them all myself.

635
00:20:48,330 --> 00:20:49,400
Xia Xiaolan's clothing store

636
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,730
is opening soon, right?

637
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,320
Remember to send a flower basket.

638
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:52,670
No.

639
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:53,720
Send 10.

640
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,550
Arrange for 10 people to deliver them.

641
00:20:55,550 --> 00:20:56,550
Make sure to fill the whole street.

642
00:20:56,550 --> 00:20:57,350
Young Master.

643
00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:01,350
She just rented that shop.

644
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:03,640
The renovation will take

645
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:04,550
some time.

646
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:07,440
Then... I'll treat her to dinner.

647
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:10,220
To congratulate her on renting the shop.

648
00:21:10,550 --> 00:21:11,210
Okay, okay.

649
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,590
That...

650
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:15,640
That boyfriend of hers—
what's his name again?

651
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:17,440
It's Zhou... Zhou something.

652
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:18,510
Zhou Cheng.

653
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:22,410
That darn bastard in my way
should just drop dead.

654
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:24,550
Should we get someone

655
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:26,410
to make him drop dead for real?

656
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:27,920
Do you think I'm stupid?

657
00:21:28,510 --> 00:21:29,970
If he really dropped dead,

658
00:21:30,510 --> 00:21:31,680
wouldn't Xia Xiaolan

659
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:33,590
remember him for the rest of her life?

660
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:35,320
You're so smart, Young Master.

661
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,340
But later, when you have time,

662
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,680
look into him.

663
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:40,800
See what he's actually made of.

664
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:42,000
Okay.

665
00:21:43,110 --> 00:21:44,830
We are in Shengcheng now,

666
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:45,830
not Gangdao.

667
00:21:46,370 --> 00:21:47,150
Don't bring those ways

668
00:21:47,150 --> 00:21:48,070
here.

669
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:50,440
Whether it's making money
or chasing women,

670
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:51,640
my dad's ways

671
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:53,010
are totally outdated.

672
00:21:53,030 --> 00:21:53,760
Understood.

673
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:57,030
What's my dad

674
00:21:57,160 --> 00:21:58,020
up to recently?

675
00:21:58,200 --> 00:22:00,270
Master seems

676
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:01,600
to be into art recently.

677
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:03,440
He found a teacher in Gangdao

678
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,100
to learn... What was it again?

679
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:06,240
Tango.

680
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:09,280
That's good.

681
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:10,480
He should find something

682
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,550
to keep himself busy.

683
00:22:11,550 --> 00:22:12,030
Right.

684
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:14,040
Young Master.

685
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,200
Young Master.

686
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,400
It's Xia Dajun.

687
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:17,720
Young Master!

688
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:19,000
Xia Dajun?

689
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:20,310
What does he want from me?

690
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:20,830
No idea.

691
00:22:20,830 --> 00:22:22,630
I don't want to see him right now.

692
00:22:24,270 --> 00:22:25,790
Forget it. He saved my life once.

693
00:22:25,790 --> 00:22:26,480
Let him in.

694
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:26,920
Okay.

695
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:33,210
Please come in.

696
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:35,590
Dajun.

697
00:22:35,850 --> 00:22:36,310
Young Master.

698
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,160
What's the matter?

699
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:37,960
Have a seat.

700
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:38,920
No, thanks.

701
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:41,970
My family has come to Shengcheng.

702
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,240
Your family?

703
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:45,550
My mother,

704
00:22:45,890 --> 00:22:47,020
my younger brother,

705
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:47,830
his wife,

706
00:22:48,120 --> 00:22:48,760
and their kid...

707
00:22:48,760 --> 00:22:50,070
Alright, alright, I get it.

708
00:22:50,070 --> 00:22:51,270
Just get to the point.

709
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,480
Here's the thing.

710
00:22:55,070 --> 00:22:56,800
They've been here for 2 months.

711
00:22:57,750 --> 00:22:59,010
We bought some things,

712
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:01,040
and I'm running short on money.

713
00:23:01,710 --> 00:23:02,920
Young Master, do you think

714
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:05,180
I could get an advance on next month's...

715
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,350
Got it, got it.

716
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:08,440
Hua.

717
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:09,610
Go to accounting

718
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:11,900
and advance two months' salary to Dajun.

719
00:23:12,270 --> 00:23:13,440
O-Okay.

720
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,270
Thank you so much, Young Master.

721
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:16,640
Thank you very much.

722
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:17,890
You're welcome.

723
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,200
But Dajun,

724
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:21,480
you've been with me in Shengcheng

725
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,740
for a while now, right?

726
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,160
I see that

727
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,270
your family is all here now,

728
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:28,040
and your old injuries haven't healed.

729
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:29,100
Why don't I arrange

730
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,640
an office job for you?

731
00:23:32,270 --> 00:23:33,110
An office job?

732
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:37,070
Young Master.

733
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:38,720
I'd rather serve you by your side.

734
00:23:38,720 --> 00:23:40,740
Working in the office is still serving me.

735
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:41,870
It's just that the hours

736
00:23:41,870 --> 00:23:42,880
will be more regular.

737
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:43,620
It'll also be easier for you

738
00:23:43,620 --> 00:23:45,150
to take care of your family.

739
00:23:45,430 --> 00:23:45,910
Hua.

740
00:23:46,170 --> 00:23:47,030
Go to the office

741
00:23:47,060 --> 00:23:48,590
and arrange a suitable position

742
00:23:48,590 --> 00:23:49,440
for Dajun.

743
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:51,400
You'll start next week.

744
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:54,580
I'll be going now.

745
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,170
Goodbye.

746
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:57,400
Go on.

747
00:23:58,590 --> 00:23:59,200
Dajun.

748
00:23:59,770 --> 00:24:00,850
Office work offers

749
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:02,000
promotions and raises.

750
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:02,600
Work hard.

751
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:05,110
Goodbye.

752
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:11,960
Young Master.

753
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:14,180
Xia Dajun can't even read.

754
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:15,900
Why let him work in the office?

755
00:24:16,030 --> 00:24:17,070
You don't even know

756
00:24:17,070 --> 00:24:17,830
how to arrange a position?

757
00:24:17,830 --> 00:24:20,360
Seems like you've lost your place
serving me.

758
00:24:20,990 --> 00:24:22,720
Then is cleaning toilets okay?

759
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:30,340
Li.

760
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,160
Where's Zhenzhu?

761
00:24:33,040 --> 00:24:34,880
Senior went with Kang Wei to get stock.

762
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,270
She asked you guys to go ahead,

763
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,320
and they'll be there in a bit.

764
00:24:37,320 --> 00:24:38,350
It's getting dark.

765
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:39,950
What stock are they getting?

766
00:24:40,030 --> 00:24:41,960
Kang Wei came over this afternoon.

767
00:24:42,080 --> 00:24:43,790
They chatted inside for a while,

768
00:24:43,790 --> 00:24:44,500
made a couple of calls,

769
00:24:44,500 --> 00:24:45,830
and then left together.

770
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,910
I think they went to the seaside.

771
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:05,070
Oh no. This is bad.

772
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:07,200
Li.

773
00:25:07,410 --> 00:25:08,200
By 8 PM tonight,

774
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,440
if we haven't returned,

775
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:09,830
call the police.

776
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:10,160
Okay.

777
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:12,410
Call the police?

778
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:18,590
You don't think those two

779
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:20,380
are actually smuggling goods, do you?

780
00:25:20,380 --> 00:25:22,160
They wouldn't have the guts, right?

781
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:22,750
Our law firm recently

782
00:25:22,750 --> 00:25:24,110
took on a smuggling case.

783
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:25,070
The files say

784
00:25:25,140 --> 00:25:25,790
there's still a large batch

785
00:25:25,790 --> 00:25:27,450
of small appliances missing.

786
00:25:28,270 --> 00:25:29,850
There are too many containers here.

787
00:25:29,850 --> 00:25:30,640
Checking them one by one

788
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:31,770
would take too long.

789
00:25:36,110 --> 00:25:37,240
Let's go over there.

790
00:25:45,640 --> 00:25:47,000
It's too dangerous here.

791
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:47,800
You stay here.

792
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:49,030
I'll go meet up with the police then.

793
00:25:49,030 --> 00:25:49,920
You stall them.

794
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:50,400
Okay.

795
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:51,210
Be careful.

796
00:25:58,620 --> 00:25:59,300
Mr. Qiao.

797
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:01,080
Let's skip the pleasantries

798
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:02,770
and get straight to the goods.

799
00:26:17,540 --> 00:26:18,880
We need to check the goods first.

800
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:20,210
You can check the goods,

801
00:26:21,270 --> 00:26:22,030
but

802
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:23,900
we have to do it elsewhere.

803
00:26:26,790 --> 00:26:27,520
Don't worry.

804
00:26:28,210 --> 00:26:29,920
For the amount of goods you want

805
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,380
and the money you brought,

806
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:34,440
I wouldn't kill you for it.

807
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:35,440
Right?

808
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:36,480
Mr. Qiao,

809
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,080
that's not what we meant.

810
00:26:38,270 --> 00:26:39,480
Since Jian introduced you to me,

811
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,680
of course I trust you.

812
00:26:40,830 --> 00:26:42,000
But we're paying

813
00:26:42,030 --> 00:26:42,790
real money

814
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:44,000
for tens of thousands worth of goods,

815
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:45,270
so we have to check.

816
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:47,570
-Then we'll feel more assu...
-Kang!

817
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:51,880
You really have the guts

818
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:53,810
to do business behind my back, huh?

819
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:56,640
What's this supposed to mean?

820
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,970
I'm here to do business.

821
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:04,640
Big business.

822
00:27:08,270 --> 00:27:09,930
I really am here for business.

823
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,240
What,

824
00:27:18,960 --> 00:27:19,850
did you two really think

825
00:27:19,850 --> 00:27:20,270
you could call the shots

826
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:21,350
on this deal?

827
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:23,550
If Li hadn't tipped me off,

828
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,510
I wouldn't have caught you two

829
00:27:25,510 --> 00:27:27,970
embezzling merchandise funds red-handed.

830
00:27:28,070 --> 00:27:28,930
Who is this guy?

831
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,190
Who am I?

832
00:27:33,270 --> 00:27:34,130
Let me tell you—

833
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,240
I'm the real boss.

834
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:38,320
Why do business with them

835
00:27:39,070 --> 00:27:40,470
when you can do it with me?

836
00:27:40,510 --> 00:27:41,790
Whatever they're paying,

837
00:27:41,790 --> 00:27:42,790
I'll pay double.

838
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:45,000
But

839
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:46,960
tell these two

840
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:49,400
to get the hell out of here right now!

841
00:27:49,980 --> 00:27:51,160
I'm absolutely not doing business

842
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,370
with these backstabbing bastards

843
00:27:52,370 --> 00:27:53,610
anymore.

844
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:02,410
Who's leaving is yet to be seen.

845
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:04,110
You think you're so tough

846
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:05,360
with your stinking money?

847
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:06,440
Let's see if you can pull off this deal

848
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:07,270
without me.

849
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:07,920
Mr. Qiao,

850
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:09,320
make them leave first...

851
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:42,920
Stop!

852
00:28:43,390 --> 00:28:44,220
Stop! Stop!

853
00:28:46,110 --> 00:28:46,880
Here! Here!

854
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:47,510
Officers!

855
00:28:53,310 --> 00:28:54,750
The fact that you called the police

856
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:55,680
shows you've got

857
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,680
some legal awareness.

858
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:57,200
But

859
00:28:57,790 --> 00:28:58,480
don't get overconfident

860
00:28:58,480 --> 00:29:00,350
just because
you know some fighting skills.

861
00:29:00,350 --> 00:29:01,160
These people

862
00:29:01,470 --> 00:29:02,470
are armed

863
00:29:02,830 --> 00:29:03,750
and very dangerous—

864
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,750
not something a few youngsters like you

865
00:29:04,750 --> 00:29:05,410
can handle.

866
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:06,750
We have also been

867
00:29:06,750 --> 00:29:08,350
cracking down on this group.

868
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:09,830
If anything like this happens
in the future,

869
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:11,220
call the police immediately

870
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:12,130
and wait for us to handle it.

871
00:29:12,130 --> 00:29:12,680
Understood?

872
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:13,200
Understood.

873
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:13,790
Understood.

874
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:14,440
You guys,

875
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:15,640
come back to the station with me

876
00:29:15,640 --> 00:29:17,000
and explain the situation.

877
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:17,350
Okay.

878
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:20,740
Take them away.

879
00:29:21,110 --> 00:29:21,480
Move!

880
00:29:22,110 --> 00:29:22,440
Move!

881
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:23,720
Follow up! Follow up!

882
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:24,240
Move!

883
00:29:24,350 --> 00:29:24,830
Follow up!

884
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:25,270
Move!

885
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,830
What's this?

886
00:29:27,410 --> 00:29:28,410
It's the new

887
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:30,240
24-inch color TV he bought.

888
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,790
It's huge!

889
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,960
Can we turn it on and have a look?

890
00:29:36,750 --> 00:29:37,310
Mom.

891
00:29:38,030 --> 00:29:38,680
Mom!

892
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:39,680
Mom!

893
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:41,750
Mom!

894
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,490
What are you doing?

895
00:29:43,490 --> 00:29:45,240
Why are you taking a quilt
into the kitchen?

896
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,270
I don't want to sleep with Junshan

897
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:47,270
and Junbao anymore.

898
00:29:47,270 --> 00:29:47,720
They're too noisy.

899
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:48,240
I don't want to sleep

900
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,400
with her either.

901
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,130
Shut up, both of you!

902
00:29:51,270 --> 00:29:51,880
Stop it!

903
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:56,370
Where do you want to sleep
if not with them?

904
00:29:56,370 --> 00:29:57,370
This room is tiny.

905
00:29:57,830 --> 00:29:59,490
Sleep on the floor if you want.

906
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,320
I'll sleep here!

907
00:30:01,350 --> 00:30:01,810
I'll...

908
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:03,920
Sorry, Grandma.

909
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:04,440
Oh my.

910
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:07,310
What a waste of my wine.

911
00:30:08,700 --> 00:30:10,270
Sleep wherever you want.

912
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:12,030
Just don't eye my room.

913
00:30:14,970 --> 00:30:16,500
What are you staring at

914
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,920
with your eyes wide open?

915
00:30:18,270 --> 00:30:20,680
If you don't like it, go get a job.

916
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:24,130
They cover room and board,

917
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,560
and you'll earn a salary.

918
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,140
Mother.

919
00:30:33,110 --> 00:30:34,240
Dajun, you're back.

920
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:35,080
Uncle Dajun.

921
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:36,750
Well,

922
00:30:37,510 --> 00:30:38,270
Jingui.

923
00:30:39,170 --> 00:30:40,300
Dajun, you're here.

924
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:42,000
Take these inside.

925
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:42,880
Dajun,

926
00:30:43,110 --> 00:30:43,770
have a seat.

927
00:30:45,250 --> 00:30:45,930
Dajun,

928
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:47,350
aren't you working at

929
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:49,650
that com...

930
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,610
That com-com...

931
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:51,920
It's company, Grandma.

932
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:52,850
What "com-com"?

933
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:55,400
Right. Yes, company.

934
00:30:55,730 --> 00:30:57,210
Aren't you working at

935
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,180
a big company—

936
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,680
living in a big house,

937
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:00,740
eating fancy meals,

938
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:02,070
and drinking fine wine?

939
00:31:02,270 --> 00:31:03,290
So you still remember that

940
00:31:03,290 --> 00:31:04,880
I'm living in this cramped hole?

941
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:05,440
Mother.

942
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:07,400
I live in the company dorm.

943
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:08,740
It's just one room.

944
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,160
Rent in the city isn't cheap.

945
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,920
I can't afford anything bigger.

946
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,850
Can't afford it?

947
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:16,720
So you're just telling me

948
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:18,120
you have no money, right?

949
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:19,940
Who are you trying to fool?

950
00:31:19,980 --> 00:31:21,960
You think just because I don't go out,

951
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,220
I don't know anything?

952
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:24,440
Your boss pays you

953
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,440
hundreds a month.

954
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,590
I know it perfectly well.

955
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:27,830
How dare you lie to me?

956
00:31:28,880 --> 00:31:30,830
There are so many mouths to feed,

957
00:31:31,900 --> 00:31:33,750
plus rent, groceries,

958
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:35,960
and water and electricity bills...

959
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:38,750
So you're reluctant

960
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:40,280
to buy things for me, right?

961
00:31:41,170 --> 00:31:42,200
If you're reluctant, don't buy anything.

962
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:43,750
How could I be reluctant?

963
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:46,310
Dajun.

964
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:47,750
Have some warm water.

965
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:49,640
Hongbing isn't back yet?

966
00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:51,880
Well...

967
00:31:52,150 --> 00:31:52,830
You know...

968
00:31:53,030 --> 00:31:54,560
He went out to look for a job.

969
00:31:54,690 --> 00:31:55,590
It's quite easy to find a job

970
00:31:55,590 --> 00:31:56,830
here, you know?

971
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:58,750
But there's a problem.

972
00:31:58,880 --> 00:31:59,550
The thing is,

973
00:31:59,550 --> 00:32:00,960
either the pay is too low

974
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,510
or the work is too tiring.

975
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:03,350
Back in the village,

976
00:32:03,350 --> 00:32:03,940
he injured his back

977
00:32:03,940 --> 00:32:05,340
while working, you know?

978
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:07,250
So he can't do heavy labor now.

979
00:32:07,550 --> 00:32:08,200
Jingui.

980
00:32:09,070 --> 00:32:10,720
About this matter,

981
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:12,070
for our Dajun,

982
00:32:12,070 --> 00:32:13,200
it's nothing at all.

983
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:16,680
As the old saying goes,

984
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:21,160
"once a man hits it big,
his whole family benefits."

985
00:32:21,770 --> 00:32:22,610
Our Dajun

986
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,170
once saved his boss's life.

987
00:32:24,290 --> 00:32:25,520
That makes our whole family

988
00:32:25,520 --> 00:32:27,320
his boss's benefactors, right?

989
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:28,830
Right, right.

990
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:30,610
I forgot about that.

991
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:31,440
Well,

992
00:32:31,590 --> 00:32:33,350
go back and tell your boss

993
00:32:33,750 --> 00:32:35,880
that I said

994
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:38,050
to give our Hongbing

995
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,790
a job by his side.

996
00:32:40,590 --> 00:32:41,560
He's not in good health,

997
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:42,520
so no heavy work.

998
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:43,160
Right, right.

999
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,440
He can't do heavy labor.

1000
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:46,200
Why turn down easy money, right?

1001
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,600
Why shouldn't we earn it?

1002
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,730
Even a little money is fine.

1003
00:32:51,610 --> 00:32:52,130
Mother.

1004
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:54,590
I borrowed this from my boss.

1005
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,560
My boss assigned me a new job,

1006
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:59,270
so I'll have more time

1007
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,930
to take care of you from now on.

1008
00:33:02,070 --> 00:33:03,880
That's the way!

1009
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:05,480
Earn more money in the future,

1010
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:06,810
and bring me more money.

1011
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:09,810
That's the best way to show
your filial respect to me.

1012
00:33:11,390 --> 00:33:12,350
Mother, take your time eating.

1013
00:33:12,350 --> 00:33:13,280
I'm leaving now.

1014
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,030
Dajun!

1015
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:16,930
About Hongbing's work,

1016
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:18,270
don't forget about it!

1017
00:33:18,530 --> 00:33:19,370
You... You...

1018
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,960
Look at you, so clueless.

1019
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:23,020
Hurry up and see your Uncle Dajun out.

1020
00:33:23,670 --> 00:33:25,030
Why are you still standing there?

1021
00:33:25,030 --> 00:33:26,070
-Uncle Dajun!
-Seriously.

1022
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:27,130
Let me walk you out!

1023
00:33:37,510 --> 00:33:37,960
Well,

1024
00:33:37,960 --> 00:33:39,490
don't look so down, you all.

1025
00:33:39,720 --> 00:33:40,130
Look,

1026
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:40,790
we've been through

1027
00:33:40,790 --> 00:33:42,390
life and death together now.

1028
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:45,450
Stop there!

1029
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:46,550
Sis Bai!

1030
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:47,880
Bro, stop chasing! Stop!

1031
00:33:47,880 --> 00:33:48,610
Are you okay?

1032
00:33:48,750 --> 00:33:49,480
Are you okay?

1033
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,030
Who are you?

1034
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:51,760
I surrender.

1035
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,070
I stole something.

1036
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:53,750
Speak properly.

1037
00:33:53,750 --> 00:33:55,280
This is the police station.

1038
00:33:56,750 --> 00:33:57,310
Comrade.

1039
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:58,720
Are you all right?

1040
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:00,440
Let me take a look.

1041
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:02,530
Hey, what are you doing?

1042
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:03,030
I...

1043
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,690
It was dislocated.

1044
00:34:07,690 --> 00:34:08,670
I just set it back in place for you.

1045
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:09,469
Try moving it.

1046
00:34:15,350 --> 00:34:16,679
You'd better go to the hospital
for an X-ray.

1047
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:17,449
to rule out

1048
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:18,880
any further bone issues.

1049
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:25,100
Th-Thanks.

1050
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:26,960
Officer.

1051
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:27,440
Are you okay?

1052
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:28,170
He's a thief.

1053
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:29,400
I saw him stealing.

1054
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:30,560
I'm a witness.

1055
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,510
I'm the thief.

1056
00:34:31,510 --> 00:34:32,630
What happened to your face?

1057
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:34,290
I... I fell and hurt it myself.

1058
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,520
You two, come with me.

1059
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:36,360
Okay.

1060
00:34:43,909 --> 00:34:44,960
Alright, let's go.

1061
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:45,400
Go on.

1062
00:34:46,050 --> 00:34:46,630
Let's go.

1063
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:51,440
Sis Bai.

1064
00:34:52,230 --> 00:34:52,920
Sis Bai?

1065
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:57,220
What are you doing? Waiting for
another thief to bump into you?

1066
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:16,590
Sis Bai has the best fighting skills,

1067
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:18,450
yet Sis Bai is the one who got hurt.

1068
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:23,760
Didn't you say there'd be

1069
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,890
absolutely no issues with this batch?

1070
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:28,050
You call this "no issues"?

1071
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,400
If Zhou Cheng hadn't

1072
00:35:30,430 --> 00:35:32,230
brought the police there today,

1073
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:34,230
either these goods would be confiscated

1074
00:35:34,230 --> 00:35:35,510
and our hard-earned money

1075
00:35:35,510 --> 00:35:36,840
would go down the drain,

1076
00:35:37,050 --> 00:35:38,150
or we'd have to sell them secretly,

1077
00:35:38,150 --> 00:35:39,000
basically becoming accomplices

1078
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:41,190
to smugglers in selling smuggled goods!

1079
00:35:41,190 --> 00:35:42,760
If your business fails,

1080
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,070
you can go back to Jingcheng.

1081
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:44,920
But what about me?

1082
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,450
Did you ever think about me?

1083
00:35:47,110 --> 00:35:48,760
You almost ruined me!

1084
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,320
Sis Bai.

1085
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:56,130
Wei was also scammed, you know.

1086
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,000
Wei.

1087
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,910
You can't blame Sis Bai for being angry.

1088
00:36:02,190 --> 00:36:03,790
It's one thing to lose money;

1089
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:06,180
but today, you put your safety in danger.

1090
00:36:08,030 --> 00:36:09,090
So what should I do?

1091
00:36:10,550 --> 00:36:12,150
Then tell me what I should do!

1092
00:36:12,830 --> 00:36:13,720
Don't you think I feel bad

1093
00:36:13,720 --> 00:36:14,580
that things turned out like this?

1094
00:36:14,580 --> 00:36:15,470
Did I want this?

1095
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:18,490
I've been in Shengcheng for a month,

1096
00:36:18,490 --> 00:36:19,360
running around like a headless chicken

1097
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,940
without accomplishing anything!

1098
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:21,500
My uncle

1099
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,970
came all the way here a few days ago

1100
00:36:22,970 --> 00:36:23,630
and scolded me!

1101
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:25,030
He wanted me to go back with him,

1102
00:36:25,030 --> 00:36:25,920
but I refused!

1103
00:36:26,230 --> 00:36:26,960
I just wanted to prove

1104
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:28,360
that my choice was right!

1105
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:53,040
Wei just came to Shengcheng.

1106
00:36:53,410 --> 00:36:54,480
He really didn't know

1107
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,960
how complicated things are here.

1108
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:56,920
But you're different.

1109
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:58,520
How could you be so careless?

1110
00:37:00,010 --> 00:37:00,850
I know

1111
00:37:00,870 --> 00:37:02,800
this wasn't entirely Wei's fault.

1112
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:04,000
My shop just opened,

1113
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:05,850
business hasn't picked up,

1114
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,510
and we lost money recently.

1115
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:09,030
So I got anxious.

1116
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:11,990
Why didn't you come to me?

1117
00:37:12,150 --> 00:37:12,710
We all

1118
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:14,200
have own own things to do,

1119
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:15,710
and we all need money.

1120
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:16,710
I thought

1121
00:37:17,290 --> 00:37:18,150
if I could solve it myself,

1122
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:19,480
I shouldn't bother you.

1123
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,450
Alright.

1124
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:50,740
That's enough.

1125
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:54,480
Sis Bai.

1126
00:37:55,710 --> 00:37:56,320
I failed

1127
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,230
your trust.

1128
00:37:58,920 --> 00:37:59,920
The money we lost—

1129
00:38:00,030 --> 00:38:01,690
I'll definitely earn it back.

1130
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,360
I'll do it the right way—

1131
00:38:03,670 --> 00:38:05,000
honestly and steadily.

1132
00:38:08,110 --> 00:38:09,710
The first step is always the hardest,

1133
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:11,150
but it won't always be like this.

1134
00:38:11,150 --> 00:38:13,230
Miracles happen every day in Shengcheng.

1135
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,320
Why can't it be us?

1136
00:38:14,710 --> 00:38:15,110
Right.

1137
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:16,650
I just want to prove

1138
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:17,930
that the path I chose

1139
00:38:18,190 --> 00:38:19,120
is the right one.

1140
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:20,340
Kang Lianming!

1141
00:38:20,350 --> 00:38:28,320
♪ The stars flow across the sky,
and I walk this road with you ♪

1142
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:23,630
You can't look down on me!

1143
00:38:26,570 --> 00:38:28,190
If you eat salted fish,
you must bear the thirst.

1144
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,840
Endure the hard times,
and good days will come.

1145
00:38:29,130 --> 00:38:33,070
♪ From strangers,
our hearts slowly grow close ♪

1146
00:38:31,190 --> 00:38:32,320
What's that you're saying?

1147
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,210
I believe in you.

1148
00:38:33,210 --> 00:38:36,590
♪ Quietly, we treat each other
with sincerity ♪

1149
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:36,290
We'll definitely live a good life.

1150
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:37,490
Come on!

1151
00:38:37,560 --> 00:38:45,480
♪ Life is like a dream,
and friends are like a mist ♪

1152
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,320
We must knock all those

1153
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,400
who look down on us

1154
00:38:40,630 --> 00:38:41,400
down!

1155
00:38:41,590 --> 00:38:42,440
Knock them down!

1156
00:38:42,440 --> 00:38:42,840
Right!

1157
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:44,960
Don't look down on the poor youth!

1158
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,550
We're not really poor, though.

1159
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:46,960
Right.

1160
00:38:46,640 --> 00:38:50,420
♪ True confidants are rare,
after storms and trials ♪

1161
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,230
You know what I mean.

1162
00:38:48,230 --> 00:38:50,640
Alright then.
Don't look down on the poor youth,

1163
00:38:50,640 --> 00:38:57,540
♪ The one who never steps back for me,
that is you ♪

1164
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:53,380
don't look down on
the inexperienced youth,

1165
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:55,760
and don't look down on the youth
whose ambitions are yet unfulfilled!

1166
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:58,480
Don't look down on the youth
whose ambitions are yet unfulfilled!

1167
00:38:58,280 --> 00:39:02,210
♪ In the distant night sky,
the scattered stars are all connected ♪

1168
00:39:02,240 --> 00:39:07,740
♪ Even if the road ahead
is full of thorns ♪

1169
00:39:08,580 --> 00:39:11,710
♪ You help untangle
the loneliness in my heart ♪

1170
00:39:11,740 --> 00:39:15,300
♪ Who truly understands me? ♪

1171
00:39:15,640 --> 00:39:16,480
Watching my lover

1172
00:39:15,700 --> 00:39:19,610
♪ Like two hands,
together in joy and in sorrow ♪

1173
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:17,820
and my good friends

1174
00:39:18,030 --> 00:39:19,030
argue together,

1175
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:19,800
mess around together,

1176
00:39:19,640 --> 00:39:25,320
♪ We share everything,
never dividing between you and me ♪

1177
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:22,570
and want to take on the whole world
together—

1178
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:23,960
I wouldn't have even dared to imagine

1179
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,490
such a passionate,
almost cringey kind of scene

1180
00:39:25,490 --> 00:39:27,550
in my past life.

1181
00:39:26,110 --> 00:39:30,250
♪ You for me, and I for you ♪

1182
00:39:31,060 --> 00:39:37,210
♪ Facing hardship and despair together,
tightly holding your hand ♪

1183
00:39:38,070 --> 00:39:42,260
♪ My friend ♪

1184
00:39:53,110 --> 00:39:55,440
Those two must have been terrified today.

1185
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:57,530
You were terrified too, right?

1186
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:23,270
What are you thinking about?

1187
00:40:26,070 --> 00:40:27,190
I was wondering

1188
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,480
if I made starting a business

1189
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:30,510
seem too simple.

1190
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:33,580
I thought having ideas

1191
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:34,840
and courage

1192
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,900
was enough to forge ahead.

1193
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:39,280
But I forgot

1194
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:43,290
that while this place
is full of opportunities,

1195
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:45,030
it's also full of traps.

1196
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:48,150
Was it because I seemed too confident

1197
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:49,190
about everything

1198
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:52,400
that I made everyone let their guard down?

1199
00:41:00,770 --> 00:41:01,670
You're not some kind of

1200
00:41:01,670 --> 00:41:03,200
all-knowing god after all.

1201
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,280
When young people start a business,

1202
00:41:05,280 --> 00:41:07,480
who hasn't gone through
their share of hardships?

1203
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,080
Look at us—

1204
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:10,040
being here together,

1205
00:41:10,400 --> 00:41:11,860
working hard side by side—

1206
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:13,860
isn't that the best thing?

1207
00:41:17,190 --> 00:41:17,670
Yes.

1208
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:21,220
Though Wei and Zhenzhu

1209
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:22,560
were a bit impulsive,

1210
00:41:23,120 --> 00:41:23,840
it also proves

1211
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,500
that they still have courage.

1212
00:41:25,890 --> 00:41:27,080
In the day-to-day

1213
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:28,710
hustle for life,

1214
00:41:29,450 --> 00:41:30,850
the easiest thing to lose

1215
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:31,840
is courage.

1216
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,510
I have a friend.

1217
00:41:39,710 --> 00:41:41,400
Since her family was poor,

1218
00:41:42,240 --> 00:41:44,040
she's always relied on herself.

1219
00:41:45,150 --> 00:41:47,210
From university into the workforce,

1220
00:41:47,510 --> 00:41:49,570
she's cherished every opportunity,

1221
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:55,190
working hard

1222
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:57,330
while treading carefully.

1223
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:59,630
She was afraid of making mistakes,

1224
00:41:59,630 --> 00:42:01,230
afraid of offending people,

1225
00:42:01,450 --> 00:42:03,910
afraid that the hard-earned opportunities

1226
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:04,760
she's finally gotten

1227
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,220
might suddenly slip away.

1228
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:09,150
And yet, even so,

1229
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:11,740
she still hasn't gained respect,

1230
00:42:12,360 --> 00:42:13,290
and things still

1231
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:16,090
haven't gone smoothly for her.

1232
00:42:17,230 --> 00:42:18,630
But that's not her fault.

1233
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:21,280
No one knows right from the start

1234
00:42:22,030 --> 00:42:23,490
which path to take in life.

1235
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,480
We all take detours.

1236
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:28,920
But

1237
00:42:30,110 --> 00:42:31,170
we've got friends,

1238
00:42:32,030 --> 00:42:32,750
family,

1239
00:42:38,400 --> 00:42:39,260
and loved ones,

1240
00:42:41,320 --> 00:42:42,650
so we won't lose our way.

1241
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:48,440
I know.

1242
00:42:52,940 --> 00:42:54,400
Although we make mistakes

1243
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:56,250
and face difficulties,

1244
00:42:56,920 --> 00:42:58,000
we must never

1245
00:42:58,030 --> 00:42:59,070
lose our edge.

1246
00:43:00,320 --> 00:43:00,980
Zhou Cheng,

1247
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:03,000
the same goes for you.

1248
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:04,840
If there's something you want to do,

1249
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:05,570
just go for it

1250
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:07,210
and fight for it.

1251
00:43:08,030 --> 00:43:09,110
We may be young,

1252
00:43:10,030 --> 00:43:10,920
but we're just as capable.
